    "results": "<h3>1 &amp; 2. Main Results And Theorems</h3><div class=\"theorem-box\"><p>Decision theory for models treated as approximations, with structured models and broad misspecification uncertainty.</p></div><p><strong>Formal reading.</strong> Identify the paper's state variable (x), feasible set (mathcal F), and objective (V). The theorem characterizes (x^*\\in\\arg\\max_{x\\in\\mathcal F}V(x)), an equilibrium/fixed point, or a convergence/aggregation condition.</p>",
